VI firmly believe in man work,
p92
aVwhich is anything I don't want to do, including \u2014
p93
aV(Laughter) \u2014
p94
aVall domestic tasks,
p95
aVbut also: bug killing, trash removal, lawn care and vehicle maintenance.
p96
aVI want no part of any of that.
p97
aV(Laughter)
p98
aVPink is my favorite color.
p99
aVI enjoy fashion magazines and pretty things.
p100
aVI watch "The Bachelor" and romantic comedies,
p101
aVand I have absurd fantasies about fairy tales coming true.
